name: DISASSOCIATE - LAKENO
description: (2018) I wanted to push myself out of my comfort zone by trying to create a song and video within two days. With the help of Unreal Engine, everything rendered in real time. This song is about a feeling I go through a lot, feeling alone and disconnected from reality, especially as a neurodivergent soul. Created by Leighton McDonald (aka Lakaeno)
